ep or add JVM/native-image test setup equivalent to `--add-opens=java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED` when exercising Guice method interception, proxy generation, or other CGLIB-backed paths. Generate tests against public Guice APIs such as modules, injectors, bindings, scopes, providers, TypeLiteral, InjectionPoint, and method interceptors rather than the stale 2.1.7 internal class names.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Existing 2.1.7 tests import internal classes that are absent or renamed in 2.9.1, such as unprefixed `com.google.inject.internal.cglib.*` classes and old `com.google.inject.internal.util.MapMaker`/`Finalizable*` classes.\",\n    \"Without `--add-opens=java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED`, CGLIB-backed paths fail on JDK 25 with module access errors around `ClassLoader#defineClass`.\",\n    \"Optional `org.slf4j:slf4j-api` is declared optional/dynamically imported and is not required for core meaningful coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07a218c45259e7e4016a41f223256c8194b6b6843de2005323\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2169, "output": 847, "cacheRead": 20992, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 24008, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782706711664, "responseId": "resp_07a218c45259e7e4016a41f2185b9c8194906da2da675b93ee"}, "toolResults": []}
